headline: 3 Reasons WYNN is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Wynn Resorts has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 23.5%. The stock now trades at $107.72, marking a 26.6% gain. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
